    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish without a single stone chip or swirl mark, while the interior remains in a pristine, factory-fresh state with the original scent of premium leather and untouched upholstery. Every electronic component functions perfectly, from the intuitive infotainment system to the heated seating. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service history and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage, the mechanical performance is silent, powerful, and smooth. The engine bay is immaculate, reflecting the high standard of care this car has received. It is, without exaggeration, the finest example of this model currently available on the market, offering a 'new car' experience for the discerning buyer.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
