    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, meticulously maintained in showroom condition. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L high-revving straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 12.5:1 compression ratio, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical provenance is documented, including a proactive double-VANOS overhaul and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. This example retains its factory-spec suspension geometry and variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery and traction. The exterior paint depth is consistent with original factory application, and the interior demonstrates zero delamination or bolster fatigue. A rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically flawless icon of the analog driving era.",
